Dr Sherri Tenpenny.

Dr Sherri Tenpenny is a warrior for the preservation of DNA. This means she has dedicated her life to educating and protecting us all to the dangers of invasive vaccination designed to fundamentally change who and what we are as human beings. This threat to human nature is like nothing we have faced before in all of human history. Dr Tenpenny keeps a calm head as she tirelessly fights for the most basic of all human rights: for us to remain human. 

She follows the philosophy of ‘Do no harm’ and is an advocate for personal choice especially in regards to the issue of vaccination.

Follow Dr Sherri Tenpenny on Instagram @drtenpenny and check out the links in her bio for a bunch of vital and enlightening articles.
